        <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>
According to the commentary, <a href="/name/nm0000151?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Morgan Freeman</a> was originally considered to play the part of Charles Morritz. The part eventually went to <a href="/name/nm0000168?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Samuel L. Jackson</a>.        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
When we are shown the doorway of the concert hall in Oxford, there is clearly a modern electric doorbell button in the door frame.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
                <hr />
    <div id="quotes" class="text-block">
        <h4>Quotes</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0000168/?ref_=tt_trv_qu"
><span class="character">Charles Morritz</span></a>:
What do you do when the thing you most wanted, so perfect, just comes?
<br />        <a href="trivia?tab=qt&ref_=tt_trv_qu"
